      ZEN <span class="footer-logo-accent">MMA</span>
    </p>

    <address class="footer-address">
      48640 Yale Rd, Chilliwack, BC V4Z 0B1<br />
      <a class="footer-address-link" href="tel:+17788356590">778-835-6590</a><br
      />
      <a class="footer-address-link" href="mailto:info@zenmartialarts.ca"
        >info@zenmartialarts.ca</a
      >
